Open Flash Chart
===============

Yet another open flash chart rails plugin:)
This plugin based pullmonkey's plugin:http://pullmonkey.com/projects/open_flash_chart

Open Flash Chart :http://teethgrinder.co.uk/open-flash-chart/index.php

Usage
=======
Install plugin
  ruby script/install http://martinx.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/plugins/open_flash_chart

Copy javascript and swf files
  rake chart:install

Include javascript file in your layout
  <%= javascript_include_tag [:defaults,] :chart %>

Using chart or open_flash_chart in view
  <%= chart width, height, url[,background]%>

Enjoy

